Problem: Cant Get My compile To function prop'erly ( it will not save any changes i make to my source ).

(optional) Rating: 1-10 prob'erly lol i feel even sad'er now :P. Because its probly not even hard to fix lol but i just cant get it to work :( .

Please HELP peeps :).

item.title: -={ Need Help With Compile ]=-
item.dc:creator: @faatnntaaf faatnntaaf
item.description:
@faatnntaaf wrote:

make sure you have jdk. If you do go to program files/ Java…
and look what version for example mine is jdk1.6.0_05
not the newest version=p . well anyways open up your compiler and it will have a path
This is an example path for my version.

IF EXIST “%programfiles%\JAVA\JDK1.6.0_04\BIN” (GOTO COM04)
For my version it should be changed to…

IF EXIST “%programfiles%\JAVA\JDK1.6.0_05\BIN” (GOTO COM04)
^

This should be how to fix your problem =p!
